defaultThe Review Process for IPCC ReportsdefaultSummarydefaultMy evidence addresses the Committee’s questions: 
default‘
defaultHas the IPCC adequately addressed criticisms of previous reports?default’ and default‘defaultTo what extent does AR5 reflect the range of views among climate scientists?default’default‘
defaultThis independent review of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC) was undertaken by the InterAcademy
default Council (IAC) under a $950,000 contract signed in April 2010 with the United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP)
default.
