defaultThe review recommended that
default:
default 
default‘
defaultLead Authors should 
defaultexplicitly document that a range of scientific viewpoints has been considered, and  coordinating Lead Authors and Review Editors should satisfy themselves that due consideration was given to properly documented alternative views
